        <p>If you are a Consumer in the EU or EEA, you have a right to withdraw from a distance contract for a digital service within <strong>14 days</strong> of conclusion of the contract without giving any reason, pursuant to the EU Consumer Rights Directive (2011/83/EU) and the Finnish Consumer Protection Act Ch. 6.</p>
